<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.4">
<l>koṭṭāy pallikkuṭṭi</l>
<l>kuṭamāṭi yulakaḷanta</l>
<l>maṭṭār pūṅkuḻal mātava ṉaivarak</l>
<l>koṭṭāy pallikkuṭṭi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Chirrup, baby gecko;</l>
<l>Mādhava with honey-filled flowers in his hair</l>
<l>Who measured the earth, having danced with pots,</l>
<l>Chirrup [for him] to come, baby gecko!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
